Description: {#DD5500}{ol}[Physical] - [Piercing]{/}{/}{nl}In development
Effect_SkillFactor: ["var sklFactor;", "", "if (skillOwner.ClassName == 'PC') {", "    var atkType = skill.AttackType;", "    var attribute = skill.Attribute;", "    var atkTypebyItem = GetSumOfEquipItem(skillOwner, atkType);", "    var attributebyItem = GetSumOfEquipItem(skillOwner, attribute);", "    sklFactor = skill.SklFactor + (skill.Level - 1) * skill.SklFactorByLevel + atkTypebyItem + attributebyItem;", "    return Math.floor(sklFactor);", "    } else {", "    sklFactor = skill.SklFactor + (skill.Level - 1) * skill.SklFactorByLevel;", "    return Math.floor(sklFactor);", "}", ""]
Effect_SpendSP: ["var basicSP = skill.BasicSP;", "var lv = skill.Level;", "var lvUpSpendSp = skill.LvUpSpendSp;", "var decsp = 0;", "", "if (basicSP == 0) {", "    return 0;", "}", "var abilAddSP = skill.SP;", "abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "var lvUpSpendSpRound = Math.floor((lvUpSpendSp * 10000) + 0.5)/10000;", "var value = basicSP + (lv - 1) * lvUpSpendSpRound;", "value = value + (value * abilAddSP);", "var zeminaLv = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_LV\");", "", "if (zeminaLv > 0) {", "    decsp = 4 + (zeminaLv * 4);", "}", "value = value - decsp;", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, \"AcrobaticMount_Buff\") == \"YES\") {", "", "    if (TryGetProp(skill, \"EnableCompanion\") == \"YES\") {", "        var acrobaticBuff = GetBuffByName(pc, \"AcrobaticMount_Buff\")", "        var acrobaticBuffLevel = GetBuffArg(acrobaticBuff)", "        var acrobaticAddSPRate = acrobaticBuffLevel * 0.1", "        value = value *(1 + acrobaticAddSPRate)", "        SetExProp(acrobaticBuff, \"ACROBATICMOUNT_SPENDSP\", Math.floor(value))", "    }", "", "}", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 1;", "}", "return Math.floor(value);"]
Name: Hoplite

Effect_SkillFactor: ["var sklFactor;", "", "if (skillOwner.ClassName == 'PC') {", "    var atkType = skill.AttackType;", "    var attribute = skill.Attribute;", "    var atkTypebyItem = GetSumOfEquipItem(skillOwner, atkType);", "    var attributebyItem = GetSumOfEquipItem(skillOwner, attribute);", "    sklFactor = skill.SklFactor + (skill.Level - 1) * skill.SklFactorByLevel + atkTypebyItem + attributebyItem;", "    return Math.floor(sklFactor);", "    } else {", "    sklFactor = skill.SklFactor + (skill.Level - 1) * skill.SklFactorByLevel;", "    return Math.floor(sklFactor);", "}", ""]
Name: Dragging Death

Description: {#DD5500}{ol}[Buff] - [Physical]{/}{/}{nl}Gives a buff that increases the damage of skills that can be used only while riding. SP consumption of riding-only skills is increased. Buff disappears if dismounted or low on SP.
Effect: Damage: Increase #{CaptionRatio}#%{nl}SP consumption: Increase#{CaptionRatio2}#%{nl}Duration: 40 sec{nl}Able to use while riding
Name: Acrobatic Mount

Description: {#DD5500}{ol}[Physical]{/}{/}{nl}Opens a shop to temper weapons and temporarily increase the attack power of a weapon.
Effect: Increases Attack by [Skill Level] + [Weapon Item Level] x [Weapon Grade]{nl} Attack Count: #{CaptionRatio2}#{nl}Duration: 1 hour
Effect_CaptionRatio2: ["var value = 2500 + skill.Level * 250 + pc.INT", "var Squire3 = GetAbility(pc, 'Squire3');", "", "if (Squire3 != null  &&  1 == Squire3.ActiveState  &&  skill.Level >= 3) {", "    value = value + Squire3.Level * 20", "}", "return value"]
Name: Weapon Maintenance

Description: {#DD5500}{ol}[Physical]{/}{/}{nl}Opens a shop to temper armor and temporarily increase defense. Improves tops, bottoms, and shields.

Effect_CaptionRatio2: ["var value = 500 + skill.Level * 50 + pc.INT", "var Squire4 = GetAbility(pc, 'Squire4');", "", "if (Squire4 != null  &&  1 == Squire4.ActiveState  &&  skill.Level >= 3) {", "    value = value + Squire4.Level * 5", "}", "return value"]

Description: {#DD5500}{ol}[Physical]{/}{/}{nl}Opens a shop to repair damaged equipment. Items can be repaired beyond their maximum durability and last longer. Shop prices increase when installed in a map with a dungeon.

Description: {#DD5500}{ol}[Physical]{/}{/}{nl}Bind all enemies, including boss monsters, to prevent them from moving.

Description: {#DD5500}{ol}[Physical]{/}{/}{nl}Set up a base camp for party members. Party members can use the base camp as storage or for teleportation. The duration of buffs used around the camp will increase.

Description: {#DD5500}{ol}[Physical]{/}{/}{nl}Set up a refreshment table to prepare dishes that temporarily increases the abilities of your party members. A refreshment table can only placed near a base camp. If the camp is removed, the refreshment table will be removed as well.
